Domestic transactions
	693 - Foreign exchange transferred to another domestic bank
		A - Source of fund from equity capital, equity investment, and foreign deposit, etc (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
			210 - Outward direct investments (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN and remittance amt is over USD 1M.)
			250 - Deposits overseas
			262 - Investments in overseas equity stocks (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			263 - Investments in overseas long-term bonds and notes (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			264 - Investments in overseas short-term notes and bills (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			266 - Outward remittance of funds for overseas deliverable forward and swap transactions (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			267 - Outward remittance of funds for overseas non-deliverable derivative transactions (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			270 - Investments in overseas real estate
			370 - Withdrawal of real estate investment by foreign nationals
			371 - Withdrawal of purchase of domestic presold house by foreign nationals
			380 - Redemption of global depository receipts (If FX with TWD, Government approval letter is required)
		B - Source of fund from external loan, external borrowing and issue overseas corporate bonds, etc (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
			220 - Outward loan investments (Government approval letter is required if BBK country is CN.)
			280 - Loan financing to non-resident abroad
			340 - Repayments of overseas borrowing
		C - Source of fund from overseas investment income (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
			440 - Interest of overseas borrowing
			441 - Surplus or dividend income of foreign nationals and overseas Chinese from equity investments in the R.O.C. (if FX with TWD or BBK country is CN, Government approval letter is required.)
			444 - Import finance related interest
			449 - Other investment income of foreign nationals (Please specify)
