		I - Source of fund from export clearance receipts (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
			701 - Prepayments for goods not yet imported
			702 - Fuel and supply payments
			704 - Payments for samples
			706 - Payments for imported goods with customs clearance not handled by payee (Supporting document is required; or select 801)
			70A - Payments for imported goods with customs clearance handled by payee
			720 - Payments for goods ordered offshore but supplied onshore (Supporting document is required; or select 802)
		Z - Source of fund from other overseas transaction receipts (Outward foreign remittances are remitted from other domestic banks, not purchased with TWD)
